{"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMultiPolygon(cm)multiPolygonWithPolygons:"},"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon\/multiPolygonWithPolygons:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon\/multipolygonwithpolygons:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"text":"Creates and returns a multipolygon object consisting of the given polygons.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"instancetype"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSArray<MLNPolygon *>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"polygons"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"polygons","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The array of polygons defining the shape."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"return-value","level":2,"text":"Return Value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A new multipolygon object."}]}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolygon":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a closed shape consisting of four or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"vertices, specified as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, and the edges that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connect them. For example, you could use a polygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"building, a lake, or an area you want to highlight."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPolygon","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolygon","title":"MLNPolygon","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolygon":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"polygons that do not overlap. For example, you could use a multipolygon shape"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to represent the body of land that consists of an island surrounded by an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll: the inner island would be one "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object, while the surrounding"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll would be another. You could also use a multipolygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"group of disconnected but related buildings."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMultiPolygon"}],"title":"MLNMultiPolygon","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolygon/multiPolygonWithPolygons:":{"title":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon\/multipolygonwithpolygons:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon\/multiPolygonWithPolygons:","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Creates and returns a multipolygon object consisting of the given polygons."}],"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic"}}}